======================================================================
PROOF: |BAD| <= 3 via domination structure analysis
======================================================================

PART 1: Mechanism for middle vertex badness
--------------------------------------------------
Middle vertex mechanism distribution:
  free_not_mid=3: 1440
  unique_mid_dom=0: 1440
  unknown: 1440

