PART 2: Why 4 bad vertices are impossible
--------------------------------------------------

--- n=6 ---
  Analyzed 11520 tournaments with >= 2 bad
  bridge_bad: 5760
  bridge_free_not_v=3: 4320
  bridge_free_not_v=4: 1440
  n_bad=2: 7200
  n_bad=3: 4320
  avg shared free cycles per bad pair: 1.79

--- n=7 ---
